Append/Prepend to configurable Drafts ‚¨áÔ∏è‚¨ÜÔ∏è

Configure Drafts you often want to add text to by storing their uuid and a title of your choice in Raycast together with an optional prefix.
You can quickly append / prepend text to the configured drafts

[Tweet link](https://twitter.com/FlohGro/status/1535200987908120576)

Run Draft Action üí®

Configure Drafts Actions you want to run from Raycast.
Depending on your configuration Raycast will ask for text input you want to provide to the Drafts Action or run the Action without any text input.

[Tweet link](https://twitter.com/FlohGro/status/1535200992773414912)

![media/FlohGro-872284152.jpg](data:image/png;base64,)

Open Drafts Workspace üåå

Configure Workspaces you want to quickly open from Raycast.
You can configure as many workspaces as you like by their name and open them from the workspaces list in Raycast.

[Tweet link](https://twitter.com/FlohGro/status/1535200995088773120)

Create Drafts Quicklink üîó

A helper to easily create additional Raycast Quicklinks for the following actions in Drafts:

- create draft
- quicksearch in Drafts
- search in drafts list
- search in Action list
- capture text window
- open dictation window
